form-element.label: Tests Message, Timer and Rule Exception Events.
form-element.value:
="You have started the test. Submit this task to continue.
A sub-process has be started which has an event-triggered exception flow from each of 3 nodes.When each of the exception flows is taken, each will send an Alert indicating Success. If for some reason the node is completed insted of triggering the exception flow, it will send a failure Alert.
The Timer Exception Event, will delay for 1 minute and then send its Success alert. The Message Exception Event will be triggered after this task is submitted. The Rule Exception Event will be triggered when a value greater than 10 is submitted with this task. "
